# SS14-Code Codex Rules

- Load `.agents/skills/ss14-art-core/SKILL.md` before repository work.
- Never edit `RobustToolbox/**`.
- Put new SS14-Art code/resources under `_Art`.
- Mark non-`_Art` changes with `Art-Start` / `Art-End`.
- Prefer prediction, localization, modular ECS, typed prototypes, and focused validation.
